DESCRIPTION:
------------
This configuration works if you store you music as follow:
 - Like the dot configuration but replacing with underscore instead of spaces 
    - For all folders and files


TREE STRUCTURE:
---------------
example-tree/
|-- Alice
|   |-- 2000.First_Album
|   |   |-- 01.Track_One.mp3
|   |   |-- 02.Track_Two.mp3
|   |   |-- 03.Track_Three.mp3
|   |   |-- cover.jpg
|   |   `-- playlist.m3u
|   `-- 2001.Second_Album
|       |-- 01.Track_One.mp3
|       |-- 02.Track_Two.mp3
|       |-- 03.Track_Three.mp3
|       |-- cover.jpg
|       `-- playlist.m3u
`-- Bob
    `-- The_Album
        |-- 01.Track_One.mp3
        |-- 02.Track_Two.mp3
        `-- 03.Track_Three.mp3

